title: Angel After The Fall #4 Comic (Newest)
description: As the first chapter in this epic tale reaches its penultimate point, Angel issues a challenge to someone-a lot of someones, actually-that he can&#039;t possibly win. Meanwhile, Spike considers changing sides as this hellish new status quo presents some opportunities he can&#039;t pass up. And we promise a shock ending more explosive than even those of the first three issues. Joss Whedon, Brian Lynch and Franco Urru continue their march through a Los Angeles truly gone to hell.
